   967	     * (1) the price and rate (for nft supply) (64 bytes) or
   968	     * (2) lien information (for NFT repay or auction buy) (288 bytes) or
   969	     * (3) lien information and market sell information (accept bid to NFT market sell) (>= 384 bytes).
